## Why this change
Current boot/restart flow in `src/gateway/boot.ts` always falls back to `'boot-startup'` when `previousSessionId` is missing, and cold boot always uses `'boot-startup'`. This can hide startup/hot-restart summaries from active UI sessions. Also, restart context currently does not persist origin channel intent, so Telegram-triggered restarts are not guaranteed to respond back to Telegram.

